  "body": "![XDO](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/e843a08be6702d347a50a33d1b609bfa3930cdbf.png)\n**XDO** is a Fabric modpack to share my mod settings for MC 1.21+\n## Warning\nSome mods might **not** work depending on your hardware specifications. _(e.g. Nvidium)_\n## Performance\nTested on same graphic settings, same seed. **Up to +116%** more FPS</p>\n![Comparison](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/bbe29bbc0b84f453c352b37c1d96880d78db9018.png)\n## Vanilla Tweaks Resource Pack\nA Vanilla Tweaks Resource Pack is included in this modpack. Visit https://vanillatweaks.net/ for more tweaks.\n\n<details>\n<summary>Mods Used [58]</summary>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/3dskinlayers\">3D Skin Layers</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/tr7zw\">tr7zw</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/animatica\">Animatica</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/FoundationGames\">FoundationGames</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/appleskin\">AppleSkin</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/squeek502\">squeek502</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/async-pack-scan\">Async Pack Scan</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/JFronny\">JFronny</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/auth-me\">Auth Me</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/axieum\">axieum</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/badoptimizations\">BadOptimizations</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/thosea\">thosea</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/black-bar-concealer\">Black Bar Concealer</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Gerrygames\">Gerrygames</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/blur-fabric\">Blur+</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Motschen\">Motschen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/capes\">Capes</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/caelthecolher\">caelthecolher</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chat-heads\">Chat Heads</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/dzwdz\">dzwdz</a> & <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Fourmisain\">Fourmisain</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chat-on-lost-focus\">Chat On Lost Focus</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/atikiNBTW\">atikiNBTW</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/chat-tools\">Chat Tools</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/70CentsApple\">70CentsApple</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/plugin/chunky\">Chunky</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/pop4959\">pop4959</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/clean-f3\">Clean F3</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/tyrannus00\">tyrannus00</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cloth-config\">Cloth Config API</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/shedaniel\">shedaniel</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/c2me-fabric\">Concurrent Chunk Management Engine</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/ishland\">ishland</a> & <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/duplexsystem\">duplexsystem</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/continuity\">Continuity</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/PepperCode1\">PepperCode1</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/cubes-without-borders\">Cubes Without Borders</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/Kir_Antipov\">Kir_Antipov</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dark-loading-screen\">Dark Loading Screen</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/A5b84\">A5b84</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/detail-armor-bar\">Detail Armor Bar</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/RedLime\">RedLime</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/dynamic-fps\">Dynamic FPS</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/juliand665\">juliand665</a> & <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/LostLuma\">LostLuma</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/entityculling\">Entity Culling</a> by <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/tr7zw\">tr7zw</a> & <a h